RenRen Reports Narrower First-Quarter Net Loss as Sales Increase 47%

-- B y   V i v e k   S h a n k a r
-- 
2011-06-21T00:39:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-21/renren-reports-narrower-first-quarter-net-loss-as-sales-increase-47-.html
Renren Inc. reported a narrower
first-quarter loss as revenues rose, led by advertising sales.  The company posted a loss of 1 cent a share for the period,
down from 5 cents a share a year ago. Revenue rose 47 percent to
$20.6 million.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
